These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, emerald, lavender, ebony
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, skateboard, boat
1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
2. the person who likes emerald is not the person driving the scooter##6
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the person driving the scooter is not the person who likes lavender##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | emerald   | ebony    | purple    | lavender |
| Sport      | boat | scooter | skateboard | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
House: cottage, townhouse, victorian, art-deco
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, sports, western, satire
1. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
2. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
3. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
4. the townhouse house is not the person watching sports movies##6
5. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the victorian house##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
7. the art-deco house is on the right of the cottage house##1
8. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | townhouse  | victorian    | cottage | art-deco    |
| Food       | satire | sports | western  | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, orange, mango, cauliflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skiing, rowing, ice-hockey
1. the person eating cauliflower is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
2. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person eating mango##6
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating asparagus##1
5. the person eating orange is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person eating asparagus is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | cauliflower       | orange  | asparagus  | mango |
| Job        | rowing | ice-hockey | skiing | parkour  |

