.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
House: tower, modern, colonial, cottage
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
3. the cottage house is not the person drinking cola##6
4. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
5. the colonial house is on the right of the modern house##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | cola | iced-tea | hot-chocolate     | lemonade |
| Transport   | modern     | colonial    | tower | cottage    |

