.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, italian, indian, dutch
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, video-games, fishing, photography
1. the french is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
3. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
4. the italian is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
5. the person who's hobby is camping is not the french##6
6. the indian is on the left of the italian##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | french        | dutch | indian | italian |
| Transport   | photography | camping | video-games     | fishing   |

