.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, country, house, techno
4 different pets are kept: fish, dog, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan folk##1
2. the fan techno is not the owner of the dog##6
3. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
5. the fan house is the fan house##1
6. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
7. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5
8. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
9. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | country | house    | folk  | techno   |
| Nationality   | pony  | turtle | dog | fish |

