.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, monopoly, bridge
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, poppy, tulip, rose
1. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
2. the person who growstulip is not the person playing snooker##6
3. the person playing chess is the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
5. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
6. the person playing snooker is the person who growsaconite##1
7. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person who growsaconite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | bridge | snooker     | monopoly | chess |
| Music-Genre   | tulip | aconite | rose      | poppy         |

