.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
City: boston, miami, hannover, hamburg
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, tulip, rose
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
7. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
8. the person traveling to miami is not the person who growsrose##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | miami  | boston        | hannover      | hamburg          |
| Job        | zinnia | poppy | rose | tulip |

