.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
House: townhouse, wooden, farmhouse, art-deco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, mirinda, hot-chocolate
1. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking fanta is not the art-deco house##6
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the farmhouse house##1
7. the townhouse house is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
8. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | townhouse  | farmhouse | art-deco    | wooden |
| Transport   | fanta | hot-chocolate | mirinda | milk  |

