.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, soul, folk, trance
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, soulerman, photographer, videographer
1. the designer is not the fan salsa##6
2. the fan trance is on the left of the fan soul##1
3. the videographer is the videographer##1
4. the fan trance is on the right of the videographer##1
5. the fan folk is not the videographer##6
6. the soulerman is not the fan soul##6
7. the videographer is in an even position##4
8. the fan folk is the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | folk | salsa        | trance  | soul     |
| Sport   | designer     | videographer | soulerman | photographer |

