.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, entrepreneur, librarian, mechanic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, chaman, fonseca, pall-mall
1. the scientist is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
2. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
3. the fonseca-smoker is not the librarian##6
4. the entrepreneur is between the pall-mall-smoker and the librarian##2
5. the librarian is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
6. the chaman-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the scientist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | librarian | entrepreneur    | scientist | mechanic |
| Music-Genre   | baccarat         | chaman | pall-mall   | fonseca     |

