.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indian, mexican, french
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, april, august
1. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
2. the french is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
3. the person who's birthday is in october is the french##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the indian##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is not the french##6
6. the indian is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
7. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
8. the colombian is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | colombian  | mexican | indian | french |
| Transport   | april | november     | august     | october    |

