2. the person who likes pink is the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who likes lavender is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is swimming##2
4. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | baseball       | swimming | sailing     | ice-hockey     |
| Movie-Genre   | white | pink       | lavender | yellow |

