3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the dancer is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
6. the lawyer is not the person who's birthday is in january##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | june | february | january | april |
| Transport   | musician   | dressmaker       | dancer    | lawyer     |

