.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
House: victorian, modern, tower, cape-cod
There 4 different types of food: corn, pineapple, cherry, lemon
1. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
2. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the person eating lemon is not the victorian house##6
5. the tower house is between the victorian house and the modern house##2
6. the cape-cod house is on the far left or far right##3
7. the cape-cod house is on the right of the victorian house##1
8. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | modern | tower | victorian | cape-cod |
| Pet     | cherry  | pineapple      | corn  | lemon       |

