4. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person traveling to colone##6
5. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | colone | paris | london      | san-francisco   |
| Transport   | cooking  | card-games   | puzzles | photography |

 